column5: I was using this new top water frog today, dont remember the name of it, but it was absolutely awesome. Only thing i got any hits on all day.  The only downside of it is it only has a single hook out the bottom of the frog which tends to result in alot more missed strikes. Im new and I missed alot.  Check it out
Sweet!! Looks like a "Panther Martin"... Where did ya pick it up from?
Cool frog     Never seen one like that before... guess you'll be using it more often from now on eh Leechman

I grabbed it up from my local canadian tire yesterday. Im ordering more just like it but with hooks out of the top.  Just bought another frog with coiled legs that extend when jigged, heading out tomorrow morning to see it work its magic.  Will let everyone know how it goes.
my favorite top water frog is the scum frog >> http://www.scumfrog.com/  and here is what it looks like in real life >>    Give em a try..( white / green / black)
